247
00:13:51,625 --> 00:13:53,875
- WHAT I SEEK IS
THUNDER, IZUCHI!

248
00:13:53,958 --> 00:13:55,291
- OH, PLEASE!

249
00:14:00,041 --> 00:14:02,958
