282
00:15:30,041 --> 00:15:31,000
- RYNER!

283
00:15:42,875 --> 00:15:44,500
- ( Ryner exclaims )

284
00:15:44,583 --> 00:15:47,333
IT'S ALL POINTLESS.

285
00:15:47,416 --> 00:15:49,416
YOU'VE GOT TO GET
OUT OF HERE, FERRIS!

286
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:50,625
RUN AS FAR AWAY AS YOU CAN!

287
00:15:50,708 --> 00:15:55,541
AH! DON'T LOOK BACK!
