303
00:16:47,458 --> 00:16:49,833
- WHAT HAVE YOU
VERMIN DONE TO RYNER?

304
00:16:52,166 --> 00:16:55,416
- I'VE FREED HIM TO RAIN
DOWN CATASTROPHE LIKE A GOD...

305
00:16:55,500 --> 00:16:57,916
