WAY TO BORE OUT A STIGMA.

307
00:17:01,666 --> 00:17:04,166
- ( Ryner laughing maniacally )

308
00:17:06,125 --> 00:17:08,458
- HAVEN'T YOU LEARNED ANYTHING?

309
00:17:08,541 --> 00:17:11,625
