AS WELL BE A CONJURER'S PROP.

323
00:18:06,541 --> 00:18:07,458
- RYNER...

324
00:18:07,541 --> 00:18:10,833
- LITTLE WORMS,
CRAWLING IN DIRT.

325
00:18:10,916 --> 00:18:12,666
( laughing )

326
00:18:12,750 --> 00:18:17,625
WRITHE IN A FLASH AND BE GONE!
LET ALL RETURN TO NOTHING!

327
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,708
- WE HAVE TO GET
OUT OF HERE, KUU.

328
00:18:24,791 --> 00:18:27,041
