329
00:18:40,916 --> 00:18:44,000
- STOP, RYNER!

330
00:18:44,083 --> 00:18:48,333
- RUN WHERE YOU WILL,
THE VOID AWAITS!

331
00:18:48,416 --> 00:18:50,708
