BY YOURSELF, RYNER?

336
00:19:08,625 --> 00:19:09,916
I KNOW I SURE WOULD.

337
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:13,916
- NOT REALLY, I MEAN
I'VE GOT ALL YOU GUYS.

338
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:16,583
- YOU KNOW, I COULD PRETEND TO
BE YOUR MOM FROM NOW ON,

339
00:19:16,666 --> 00:19:18,125
