AND I'LL RUN RIGHT TO YOUR SIDE.

341
00:19:20,916 --> 00:19:23,000
- HEY! I GET DIBS
ON BEING HIS DAD!

342
00:19:23,083 --> 00:19:24,208
- EWW...

343
00:19:24,291 --> 00:19:27,083
