TO SOME ICKY BOY.

344
00:19:27,166 --> 00:19:28,750
- I'VE BEEN DUMPED!

345
00:19:28,833 --> 00:19:30,625
- ( all laughing )

346
00:19:30,708 --> 00:19:35,125
- Man 1: RUN! HURRY!
- Man 2: GET OUT OF HERE! GO!

347
00:19:35,208 --> 00:19:37,750
- FILTHY GHOULS, I WANT
EVERY SCRAP YOU'VE PILFERED

348
00:19:37,833 --> 00:19:40,291
